#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.75"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.75:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.75:0.2"
msgid "8. Chetvāvagga"
msgstr "8. Incinerated"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 75. Bhītāsutta → bhītasuttaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts2)
msgctxt "sn1.75:0.3"
msgid "75. Bhītāsutta"
msgstr "75. Afraid"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.75:1.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsūdha bhītā janatā anekā,"
msgstr "“Why are so many people here afraid,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:1.2"
msgid "Maggo canekāyatanappavutto;"
msgstr "when the path has been taught with so many dimensions?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:1.3"
msgid "Pucchāmi taṃ gotama bhūripañña,"
msgstr "I ask you, Gotama, whose wisdom is vast:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:1.4"
msgid "Kismiṃ ṭhito paralokaṃ na bhāye”ti."
msgstr "Standing on what need one not fear the next world?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.43"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.1"
msgid "“Vācaṃ manañca paṇidhāya sammā,"
msgstr "“When speech and mind are directed right,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.2"
msgid "Kāyena pāpāni akubbamāno;"
msgstr "and you don’t do anything bad with the body"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.3"
msgid "Bahvannapānaṃ gharamāvasanto,"
msgstr "while dwelling at home with plenty of food and drink."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.4"
msgid "Saddho mudū saṃvibhāgī vadaññū;"
msgstr "Faithful, gentle, charitable, and kind:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.5"
msgid "Etesu dhammesu ṭhito catūsu,"
msgstr "standing on these four principles,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.75:2.6"
msgid "Dhamme ṭhito paralokaṃ na bhāye”ti."
msgstr "standing on the teaching one need not fear the next world.”"
